{"tid":1662932,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"懷疑自己有病 心理大神入","createTime":"2019-10-19T05:42:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T09:27:35.000Z","uid":303680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"66a47d9c751dc104b10ead8c0fd7cfcebb62f621","tid":1662932,"uid":303680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T05:42:39.000Z","msg":"平時成日個腦都好活躍 有啲野明知係錯或者有後果 但係都忍唔住做 係控制唔到加不自覺地嗰隻<br />\n仲有平時好難集中 最多集中到幾十分鐘 <br />\n以前已經會無啦啦個人好燥 加上呢排嘅事 情況仲嚴重咗 上網睇過有個病叫躁鬱症 唔知關唔關事 想睇醫生但係驚好貴 有冇邊度係平啲 想驗吓先<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3e2cbff3f0d5eda1b008170a5761f290d7800f8","tid":1662932,"uid":315185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T05:52:47.000Z","msg":"過度活躍?<br />\n<br />\n徵狀︰<br />\n專注力弱<br />\n容易受外界干擾而分散注意力<br />\n不能專注于某一項活動<br />\n做事缺乏條理，常常遺失書本、文具等<br />\n<br />\n過份活躍:<br />\n多言、不能安靜、容易興奮尖叫<br />\n多動、常手舞足蹈、把玩物件、不停搖腳、離位等<br />\n<br />\n行為衝動:<br />\n缺乏耐性<br />\n做事不考慮後果<br />\n打斷別人的說話<br />\n<br />\n利申:門外漢"},{"pid":"3cac689b892c08fb40d4bb444a41e4c659e5a488","tid":1662932,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T06:34:02.000Z","msg":"個人修養問題"},{"pid":"0e240495301fb216b53548dd06cb8b0052b2d5a1","tid":1662932,"uid":323958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T06:36:38.000Z","msg":"戒手淫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VB6qvfa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVB6qvfa.gif&h=32a32258&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a77xafa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa77xafa.gif&h=7ef9ebc0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yTRYQfa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyTRYQfa.gif&h=073bb63d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b4ca6845a6841350638d91e0afc485e03e3b33e","tid":1662932,"uid":303680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3e2cbff3f0d5eda1b008170a5761f290d7800f8","tid":1662