0","tid":1662932,"uid":303680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba16422ffb432565d693f4dfbacb157bceeb9e53","tid":1662932,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T07:54:35.000Z","msg":"有冇試過有一排好抑鬱？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:08:56.000Z","msg":"夜晚嗰陣諗起啲嘢就會 呢排都係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:51:57.000Z","msg":"你覺得好困擾咪去睇下醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實都只係食藥睇下有冇幫助<br />\n有幫助咪繼續食"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:52:56.000Z","msg":"正想驗吓 但係唔知邊度同驚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4e86a59bd2c1416605d48a839cc71aa97d96032","tid":1662932,"uid":41414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:59:39.000Z","msg":"心理病同性格使然應該點分？<br />\n<br />\n就算人格分裂都好<br />\n<br />\n應該去睇醫生係你覺得會影響到你日常生活<br />\n<br />\n又或者控制唔到自己到一個好嚴重既地步<br />\n<br />\n好多人好重脾氣<br />\n<br />\n唔一定可以話係病<br />\n<br />\n好多人好負面 同樣唔一定係病<br />\n<br />\n不過通常呢d野愈鑽牛角尖就愈難搞<br />\n<br />\n初步唔一定睇醫生<br />\n<br />\n發脾氣或者嬲個陣就深呼吸<br />\n<br />\n每次做重要決定既時候都用唔同既方法提醒自己<br />\n<br />\n例如打自己手板一下<br />\n<br />\n久而久之養成習慣就會深思熟慮"},{"pid":"ee2048a36ead829de8a04894797722a024ffd01c","tid":1662932,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09b231b779157090aca62997dd23b284a11135ce","tid":1662932,"uid":303680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6f6453b241faba0cd4a3f67954aae7c571fc88d","tid":1662932,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f61165943cc212f07f77e41d86f88753f1e3e30","tid":1662932,"uid":303680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:08:56.000Z","msg":"夜晚嗰陣諗起啲嘢就會 呢排都係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:51:57.000Z","msg":"你覺得好困擾咪去睇下醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實都只係食藥睇下有冇幫助<br />\n有幫助咪繼續食"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:52:56.000Z","msg":"正想驗吓 但係唔知邊度同驚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:02:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ha.org.hk/visitor/ha_visitor_text_index.asp?Content_ID=200261&amp;Lang=CHIB5&amp;Dimension=100&amp;Parent_ID=10088\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ha.org.hk%2Fvisitor%2Fha_visitor_text_index.asp%3FContent_ID%3D200261%26Lang%3DCHIB5%26Dimension%3D100%26Parent_ID%3D10088&d=hAhx4mZ6jCiP%2Fv5W8BSz9rTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=db6b6f49\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ha.org.hk/visitor/ha_visitor_text_index.asp?Content_ID=200261&amp;Lang=CHIB5&amp;Dimension=100&amp;Parent_ID=10088</a><br />\n精神科？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都唔知"},{"pid":"7888e8cde901467b476fc3709b16214728cbba42","tid":1662932,"uid":41414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:02:45.000Z","msg":"有時食藥只係輔助<br />\n<br />\n一個人既性格特質同壓力環境先係形成心理病既主因"},{"pid":"66e23f5c2182eb44040194cae535115010c10606","tid":1662932,"uid":41414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09b231b779157090aca62997dd23b284a11135ce","tid":1662932,"uid":303680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6f6453b241faba0cd4a3f67954aae7c571fc88d","tid":1662932,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f61165943cc212f07f77e41d86f88753f1e3e30","tid":1662932,"uid":303680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:08:56.000Z","msg":"夜晚嗰陣諗起啲嘢就會 呢排都係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:51:57.000Z","msg":"你覺得好困擾咪去睇下醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實都只係食藥睇下有冇幫助<br />\n有幫助咪繼續食"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:52:56.000Z","msg":"正想驗吓 但係唔知邊度同驚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:04:22.000Z","msg":"唔建議一黎就精神科<br />\n<br />\n可以試下睇中/西醫去講講你既問題<br />\n<br />\n如果真係有需要<br />\n<br />\n西醫應該會轉介/話你聽要點做"},{"pid":"f84a1bf2f1ad8002aa68f0a990159ca16b5aad47","tid":1662932,"uid":303680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4e86a59bd2c1416605d48a839cc71aa97d96032","tid":1662932,"uid":41414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:59:39.000Z","msg":"心理病同性格使然應該點分？<br />\n<br />\n就算人格分裂都好<br />\n<br />\n應該去睇醫生係你覺得會影響到你日常生活<br />\n<br />\n又或者控制唔到自己到一個好嚴重既地步<br />\n<br />\n好多人好重脾氣<br />\n<br />\n唔一定可以話係病<br />\n<br />\n好多人好負面 同樣唔一定係病<br />\n<br />\n不過通常呢d野愈鑽牛角尖就愈難搞<br />\n<br />\n初步唔一定睇醫生<br />\n<br />\n發脾氣或者嬲個陣就深呼吸<br />\n<br />\n每次做重要決定既時候都用唔同既方法提醒自己<br />\n<br />\n例如打自己手板一下<br />\n<br />\n久而久之養成習慣就會深思熟慮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:05:38.000Z","msg":"好...會參考吓"},{"pid":"83d41bbc25b1faa85a7e88140a37baa1967d73db","tid":1662932,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:05:42.000Z","msg":"係咪唔記得打飛機咋？"},{"pid":"d36a2fa601a45112528fc586cbdba6d838afa12e","tid":1662932,"uid":303680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66e23f5c2182eb44040194cae535115010c10606","tid":1662932,"uid":41414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09b231b779157090aca62997dd23b284a11135ce","tid":1662932,"uid":303680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6f6453b241faba0cd4a3f67954aae7c571fc88d","tid":1662932,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:51:57.000Z","msg":"你覺得好困擾咪去睇下醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實都只係食藥睇下有冇幫助<br />\n有幫助咪繼續食"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:52:56.000Z","msg":"正想驗吓 但係唔知邊度同驚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:04:22.000Z","msg":"唔建議一黎就精神科<br />\n<br />\n可以試下睇中/西醫去講講你既問題<br />\n<br />\n如果真係有需要<br />\n<br />\n西醫應該會轉介/話你聽要點做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:06:58.000Z","msg":"好。。。唔該晒"},{"pid":"b894d62488685ec8c29a162321d3e8c74f48d4b9","tid":1662932,"uid":303680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83d41bbc25b1faa85a7e88140a37baa1967d73db","tid":1662932,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:05:42.000Z","msg":"係咪唔記得打飛機咋？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:07:36.000Z","msg":"晚晚都打點會唔記得 而家懷疑自己打太多"},{"pid":"1bdd9f0fa77c3ee73be8bd2e327c02f85d0586d4","tid":1662932,"uid":224831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66a47d9c751dc104b10ead8c0fd7cfcebb62f621","tid":1662932,"uid":303680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T05:42:39.000Z","msg":"平時成日個腦都好活躍 有啲野明知係錯或者有後果 但係都忍唔住做 係控制唔到加不自覺地嗰隻<br />\n仲有平時好難集中 最多集中到幾十分鐘 <br />\n以前已經會無啦啦個人好燥 加上呢排嘅事 情況仲嚴重咗 上網睇過有個病叫躁鬱症 唔知關唔關事 想睇醫生但係驚好貴 有冇邊度係平啲 想驗吓先<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:18:26.000Z","msg":"就咁聽，都有D空泛啵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n近排發生咁多事，情緒會受影響都合理既，但係唔係有病 就未可以咁判斷住<br />\n同埋樓主你講既 有錯／有後果，但又忍唔住要做既事係咩事黎架？<br />\n如果唔方便講，都可以tg傾下啊：<a href=\"https://t.me/justtellmeee\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjusttellmeee&d=hAhx4mZ6jCiP%2Fv5W8BSz9rTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=a97bf453\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/justtellmeee</a>"},{"pid":"68f29cf56bde979babecdb651d8525b927d3e168","tid":1662932,"uid":269732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66a47d9c751dc104b10ead8c0fd7cfcebb62f621","tid":1662932,"uid":303680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T05:42:39.000Z","msg":"平時成日個腦都好活躍 有啲野明知係錯或者有後果 但係都忍唔住做 係控制唔到加不自覺地嗰隻<br />\n仲有平時好難集中 最多集中到幾十分鐘 <br />\n以前已經會無啦啦個人好燥 加上呢排嘅事 情況仲嚴重咗 上網睇過有個病叫躁鬱症 唔知關唔關事 想睇醫生但係驚好貴 有冇邊度係平啲 想驗吓先<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:24:37.000Z","msg":"太多野逼埋身拉。休息多啲啦。chur得多 太大壓力 太多野煩 人都死"},{"pid":"25fe85bfb278fee9df132ef55480d99127ad74e4","tid":1662932,"uid":269732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:24:56.000Z","msg":"try to keep a distance with.."},{"pid":"de0ee1e82e3efe26e230a1c4